qimportbz: A Mercurial extension to import patches from Bugzilla
  into your mercurial queue.

Original author: Rob Arnold

INSTALLING
----------

Run

  ./mach mercurial-setup

Or to install manually:

1) Clone this repository somewhere on your local machine:
   hg clone https://hg.mozilla.org/hgcustom/version-control-tools
2) Edit your ~/.hgrc and add the following to enable the extension:
   [extensions]
   qimportbz = /path/to/version-control-tools/hgext/qimportbz
